{"tid":756847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國製智能吸塵機械人被發現漏洞　視像鏡頭映像或可被第三者截取","createTime":"2018-07-26T10:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T06:25:36.000Z","uid":58335,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e64f287d968279b76a6686e249aa6a9594dd36be","tid":756847,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"未對有關漏洞進行修補,你明點解架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪大部分支國電器都有後門??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時智能家居產品都連上網，方便用戶操作管理，但這些連接互聯網的產品，有機會被🇨🇳🇨🇳不法🇨🇳🇨🇳份子入侵，甚至惡用。資訊保安公司就發現，有中國製具備 360 度視像鏡頭、Wi-Fi 上網的智能吸塵機械人，由於系統保護性能不足，如被黑客利用，家居每一個角落都有機會被監視。<br />\n<br />\n韓國資訊保安公司 Positive Technologies 研究🇨🇳🇨🇳人員🇨🇳🇨🇳發現，問題發生於中國廣東省東莞市智能家居公司 Diqee（締奇）生產的「360攝像頭智能打掃機械人」。這個機械人擁有一個 360 度視像鏡頭，可透過手機遙距控制，用戶可隨時留意家中的任何變化，價格為 2,999 🇨🇳🇨🇳人民幣🇨🇳🇨🇳（約港幣HK$3,500）。<br />\n<br />\n該裝置漏洞發生在「REQUEST_SET_WIFIPASSWORD」函數。如產品被黑客知悉其 MAC 網絡裝置識別位址，另用戶沒有更改裝置密碼，黑客就能利用預設登入資料（用戶名稱：admin／密碼：888888），再從破解該函數來取得系統管理者權限，從而實行黑客指定的遙距程式碼，屬 CVE-2018-10987 網絡漏洞。在此機械人中亦被發現 CVE-2018-10988 漏洞，但黑客需要在 SD 卡插糟上插上 SD 卡才可攻破。<br />\n<br />\n保安公司研究🇨🇳🇨🇳人員🇨🇳🇨🇳指，黑客有可能遠距離操控打掃機械人，或竊取鏡頭映像，令這部打掃機變成一部裝上車輪的盜聽器。<br />\n<br />\n保安公司已聯絡有關生產商，<span style=\"color: red;\">但到目前為止生產商仍未對有關漏洞進行修補</span>。打掃機械人產品附有一個物理遮蓋，想保障個人私隱的用戶可以物理方式掩蓋視像鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n保安公司指締奇生產的其他產品如戶外攝像鏡頭、智能門鐘、數碼錄影裝置，以及其 OEM 產品都可能隱藏這些漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：TechCrunch<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/22/cleaningrobot/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2Fcleaningrobot%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=7Xr0jXPxAHzVd%2F645HDZxf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=477e668c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/22/cleaningrobot/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"d7bbb78b81e793f46f9e6925394507ed5367c39c","tid":756847,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60dbd6025614cf6ccf0bdae61c94a924c00f268","tid":756847,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b59fccd703de1302e626ab3debacafd062db5810","tid":756847,"uid":30633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:03:40.000Z","msg":"全家人換衫的video 上晒北京<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5caf6909bdcf63246e0bbaf9d7affafa7f59fb","tid":756847,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"3721"},{"pid":"1e93d50aa7b631ccb939ebbcdb765dfc1f2f01e5","tid":756847,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"支那電器 有鏡頭 有咪 有連網就有監控"},{"pid":"4aa995ff4a1012219e1589cb28da9e08f89fc21e","tid":756847,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e93d50aa7b631ccb939ebbcdb765dfc1f2f01e5","tid":756847,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"支那電器 有鏡頭 有咪 有連網就有監控"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"但聽講鍵盤都有喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b3b8740628265f287649dbed34e5f670454d57","tid":756847,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"在中國就唔係漏洞啦"},{"pid":"b32d7fc253e1fa5e8123b89c057644886e42bf24","tid":756847,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead